00:33:48.568 --> 00:33:50.946  position:30.95%,start  align:start size:48.10%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Elim wasn't my aide.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1130
00:33:50.946 --> 00:33:54.491  position:30.95%,start  align:start size:48.10%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>He was... my friend.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1131
00:33:54.491 --> 00:33:56.869  position:30.95%,start  align:start size:48.10%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>We grew up together.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1132
00:33:56.869 --> 00:33:59.245  position:21.43%,start  align:start size:65.24%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>We were closer than brothers.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1133
00:33:59.245 --> 00:34:03.166  position:23.33%,start  align:start size:65.24%  line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>For some reason, Enabran Tain</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1134
00:33:59.245 --> 00:34:03.166  position:30.95%,start  align:start size:48.10%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>took a liking to us.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1135
00:34:03.166 --> 00:34:05.168  position:38.57%,start  align:start size:32.86%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Before long,</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1136
00:34:05.168 --> 00:34:08.296  position:21.43%,start  align:start size:67.14%  line:79.29% 
