1137
00:34:05.168 --> 00:34:08.296  position:29.05%,start  align:start size:51.90%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>in the Obsidian Order.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1138
00:34:08.296 --> 00:34:10.924  position:36.67%,start  align:start size:36.67%  line:79.29% 
