1140
00:34:10.924 --> 00:34:14.135  position:55.71%,start  align:start size:34.76%  line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Even the Guls</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1141
00:34:10.924 --> 00:34:14.135  position:55.71%,start  align:start size:29.05%  line:84.62% 
