1148
00:34:26.523 --> 00:34:29.192  position:32.86%,start  align:start size:44.29%  line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Fingers were being</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1149
00:34:26.523 --> 00:34:29.192  position:36.67%,start  align:start size:36.67%  line:84.62% 
