1165
00:35:03.727 --> 00:35:06.354  position:38.57%,start  align:start size:32.86%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>(</c.mono_sans></c.white><i><c.white><c.mono_sans> chuckles</c.mono_sans></c.white></i><c.white><c.mono_sans> )</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1166
00:35:06.354 --> 00:35:09.858  position:32.86%,start  align:start size:42.38%  line:79.29% 
