00:35:13.528 --> 00:35:19.952  position:21.43%,start  align:start size:67.14%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>to do to Elim, my best friend.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1172
00:35:19.952 --> 00:35:23.455  position:23.33%,start  align:start size:63.33%  line:79.29% 
